title: John Fitzgerald Kennedy National Historic Site: News
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     News             News       John Fitzgerald Kennedy National Historic Site makes every effort to keep the public informed about news events, special and recurring events, projects, and accomplishments which occur within and around the units of the park service.    Past news releases can also be found in the news archive. For all press inquiries, contact the park's Supervisory Ranger at (617) 566-7937, x10 or by e-mail.                 Sorry, there are no news items currently listed.
